com.soa.security

Interface ISubjectCategory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.security.Principal, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SubjectCategory

    public interface ISubjectCategory
extends java.security.Principal, java.io.Serializable
    This interface represents a specific subject category when the security context involves multiple users.
